    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Chartocinus rarus n. gen., n. sp., holotype male (2.9 x 3.1 mm) (MZB Cru 5342), Papua, Indonesia. A, overall dorsal habitus; B, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5886540/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5886544>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Chartocinus rarus n. gen., n. sp., holotype male (2.9 x 3.1 mm) (MZB Cru 5342), Papua, Indonesia. A, dorsal view of carapace (setae not drawn); B, frontal view showing left antennule, antenna, orbit, proepistome and epistome (setae not drawn); C, right third maxilliped (setae not drawn); D, thoracic sternum and sternopleonal cavity; E, pleon (setae not drawn); F, left chela; G–J, P2–P5, respectively; K, left G1 (dorsal view); L, left G1 (ventral view); M, left G2. Scales: A, D, F–J = 0.5 mm; B, C, E = 0.2 mm; K–M = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5886544/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

